Participation
Class ApplicationLogic.Counter

java.lang.Object
  Participation.ApplicationLogic.Counter
Enclosing class:
ApplicationLogic
static class ApplicationLogic.Counter
extends java.lang.Object

An inner class to keep track of fresh IDs for customer, service, and participation. A fresh ID is needed when we add e.g. a new customer. He will need an ID.

There will be 1x current Counter. Whenever we create a customer, or a service, etc, this Counter will be consulted, and updated accordingly. We will also keep it persisted in the database.
